00:14:52.696 --> 00:14:54.766 A:middle
Now, what am I talking
about here?

00:14:55.896 --> 00:15:01.646 A:middle
Well, in our new modern
multitasking-based world we have



00:14:55.896 --> 00:15:01.646 A:middle
Well, in our new modern
